Hi David

On 15-Jul-99, David McMinn wrote:
>> I just saw the command "request" in another program
>> but it doesn`t seem to work here with my blitz config. What do i need to
>> be able to run the command "request" ?
> 
> You must be missing one of the external libraries. Its the ElmoreSysLib,
> which was distributed on all/most of the BUMs. I don't think its available
> for download anywhere though.

The "Request" command is also found in the file "elmorelib.lha" in
Aminet/dev/basic  along with most of the other Elmore library commands. 
The only difference is that they are all in one library, rather than in
smaller separate ones like the later versions.

The rest of the Elmore commands are in "DosElmoreLib22.lha", also found in
dev/basic. 

Later...
