On 27-Jul-99, Rob Hutchinson wrote.

> Hello, and what not,
> 
>   In my attempt to get into the basics of ASM, I tried the
> attached and it dont appear to work. Can one of you ASM-Heads
> tell me why it gives a different value everytime I run it??
> And please explain to me what I`m doing wrong?
> 
> Thanks
> 


well the problem is that you didn't use proper addressing mode. :)

Function.b ArseHole{B.l}
  MOVE.l D0,A0            ;This was move d0,a0 which is same as
  MOVE.b (A0),D0        ;move.w d0,a0
  AsmExit
End Function

MouseWait
End

-- 

       Sami Näätänen
       EMail: sami.naatanen@dlc.fi



