Hi Ayar

On 06-Jul-99, Ayar Baboon wrote:
> Hello
>     I.R. Baboon want to cycle colours! I.r. Baboon R in Blitz mode! I.R.
> cycling palette (I.R. only having one palette, id# R being '0'), but
> changes R never not appearing on screen!
> How R i doing this? Stoopid weasel r already cycling colours!

Did you try the CyclePalette command?  If your palette doesn't have cycling
info in it already, you must use SetCycle first to set up the cycling
parameters.

The CyclePalette command just changes the colour info in the palette - then
you must use DisplayBitmap command to show the changes.

Later...
