@ENDNODE
@NODE "Mail_208" "Re: File to Newtype"
From: Sami =?iso-8859-1?Q?N=E4=E4t=E4nen?= <sami.naatanen@dlc.fi>
Date: Fri, 23 Jul 1999 10:17:44 +0300
Subject: Re: File to Newtype
Encoding: 8bit
X-UIDL: 87d05d07043553696a1bdff7b623035f

On 21-Jul-99, Curt Esser wrote.

> So, we make our NewType:
> 
> NewType.record1
>  string.l     ;8 bytes
>  morestring.l ;8 bytes
>  morestr2.l   ;8 bytes
>  morestr3.l   ;8 bytes
> End NewType

Well why not like this?

newtype.myrec
 var1.w
 var2.l
 var3.w
 string.b[32]
 string2.b[32]
end newtype

-- 

       Sami Näätänen
       EMail: sami.naatanen@dlc.fi



