> Would the ID be the same for different GFX cards?

No, it's different for each Amiag system. Which is why I created the
AutoCyberGraphXFinder, which finds the correct modeid for the requirements
you put in. ie.

    modeid.l=FindCyberMode{800,600,8}

That's width, height and depth.

If you want that, give me a shout....I did post it to the list, not sure
though.

