@NODE "Mail_310" "MUI Custom Requester V1.1"
From: Rob Hutchinson <loki@sds.in2home.co.uk>
Date: Sun, 11 Jul 1999 20:51:14 +0100
Organization: Satanic Dreams Software.
Subject: MUI Custom Requester V1.1
X-UIDL: eb0e0afa3867b384e147ed881c2e77bf

--BOUNDARY.272916992.1

Hello, and what not,

   Attached is my MUICustomRequest{} routine and all its components.
I`m all ready to upload it to aminet. Can the MUI coders in here please
test it for me? I just want to know if there are any major cockups
before I upload it.

   The reason I wrote it is mainly cos I had problems with MUIRequest
Crashing all the time, i wrote it a while back for a utility I was working
on at the time, so I`ve just updated it a bit for another utility I`m
now working, and have decided to release it.

Thanks in advance.
Hope this is usefull to people, I personally think the general design is
a lot better than the normal MUI requester!! :)

-- 

Rob,
