Funny really, that you should bring that up, coz I remember back when the AMiGA came to Denmark, how everyone was calling it "Help, my  C=128 has grown." Infact back then we had a situation pretty close to what we have now, I even remember quite alot of people whineing about how there was no "GO64" command in the AMiGA. It was an outrage ! Strange how little things change in 15 years.

Allthough Jim & Co. are really in deep shit if they don't get the games industry hooked on this baby...

Nothing sold more PC's than DOOM and Quake.

Nothing sold more Playstations than Tekken and Wipeout.

Nothing sold more N64's than Golden Eye and Shadow of the Empire.

IMHO AMiGA Inc. should get the exclusive rights to a "must have" title, and bundel it with the machine...


Greets,
