Subject: ObtainBestPen_-Example
X-UIDL: 25adc783b480ab2a76f8db166889ef02

--BOUNDARY.19563912.2

Hello,

I have had a few mails asking for the example of using the 'ObtainBestPenA_'
Included is an example which uses the RIDatatype lib, all that it is needed for
is to load a picture & palette, so is easily changed to use ILBM commands
instead (if you haven't got it).

Anybody got any improvements or better ways of doing it?

Cya,

    Leigh.

