Hello Daniel

On 01-Jul-99, Daniel Allsopp set out across the seas with this message:

In case it makes any differance now, this is what happenned on my machine :

DA>>>     - Blitz2 standard

Error message saying couldn't open window popped up.

DA>>>     - Blitz2 + NCS

A several-second pause before each drawing of the cycle gadget ie open window,
pause, draw gadgets --> click cyclegadget, pause, draw cyclegadget.

However the cycle's contents were empty.

DA>>>     - PowerBasic

Same pause, but this time only happenned when closing the Surprise! window =]

Considering it still worked better than the Blitz related programs - well done
=]

Regards
