    Hi Curt, 

> All work correctly here, except:
> 
> Bitmap - flickers very bad

    It's normal :). Look at the code, I've done a 'CLS x' so one bitmap
is totally of another colour, -> flicker (50 fps though, so a niiiiiice
flickering :-)
 
> Palette - output window says "8colour 3:255,177,51"
>          should be          "colour 3: .......

    Sorry, but it's normal too, the PrintNum() function don't have a
feedline stuff, so it's not a bug, but a programming mistake. Thanks
to report it :)

            Good bye,
 
-- 

