Well, I`ll explain again:

#Timer# gives you the time since the miggy was switched on right?,... Yes.
Well, what are the chances of you firing up your game at the exact
same milisecond as the last time? 100000 to 1 about.. Thats as random as
it gets... So the seed is determined from the timer, and numbers after
it are random.. Viola. :)

