On 14-Jul-99, Ayar Baboon wrote:

>> Statement: RESETTIMER 
>> *********************
>>      Syntax: ResetTimer  
>>       Modes: Amiga or Blitz
>> Description: 
>> Resets the Amiga's hardware timer to zero "ticks." 
>> Read the description
>> for "TICKS" for more information.
> 
