@NODE "Mail_450" "Re: Random Numbers (or are they????) Good question :)"
From: Donovan Reeve <bubby.lnk@ispi.net>
Date: Sat, 10 Jul 1999 06:40:54 +0500
Subject: Re: Random Numbers (or are they????) Good question :)
