Hello Gaz-JD/FX-s^D,
 
> Hi,
>    I've attached the complete menu code for ym RDogzII game. Howver,
> it don't BBlit the shapes onto the options menu. Can some1 take a look
> at the code and atempt to find out why please.

Use "Use Bitmap 0"  (instead of Bitmap Output 0) for the BBlits
(without the ""'s of course)

> Also, how do I make the mouse movement less sluggish?

Put a Vwait inside the Repeat/Until where you're checking the mouse
buttons.

Or, Put the little sod on a diet :)


-- 

