Hi Gaz-JD/FX-s^D,

On 06-Jul-99, you wrote:

> Hi Ayar
> On the 06-Jul-99 you said something about Re: This is frying my brain! so
> now I am going to offer a witty retort (well maybe :)
> 
> PQ: I think I have some 'smooth' scrolling map code, where the screen
> PQ: scrolls over landscape when the mouse is moved. Want it?
> 
> Nah ta :) It needs to move when the player moves the joystick/keyboard
> around, like in alien breed :)

It would't be very hard to change that.....just look for the mouse moving
code and put in some KeyCode instructions......or Joyb(1) reads.

Left Arrow Keycode = 97 
Right = 99
Up = 103
Down = 101

Something like

repeat
    VWait

    key=keycode

    select key
        case #LEFT
  
        etc. etc.

     end select

until keycode=117     ;Escape key

-- 
Cheers,
    Daniel

