--BOUNDARY.1749096920.1

Hi Donovan

On 10-Jul-99, Donovan Reeve wrote:
> On 11-Jul-99, Curt Esser flashed:
> 
>> I'm not sure what is wrong with the posted code. But I do have a very
>> nice function by David McMinn that allows printing direct to a bitmap
>> using any font you like. (This could be the Screen's bitmap).
