@NODE "Mail_602" "Window Deselction"
From: "Neil Bullock" <trogladite@trogsoft.freeserve.co.uk>
Subject: Window Deselction
Date: Mon, 19 Jul 1999 17:31:51 +0100
Organization: Trogladite Software
	charset="Windows-1252"
Encoding: 7bit
X-Info: Selby College, England
X-UIDL: 16b02a4b80abbaf4696c385666984675

Ok, has anyone got any idea how to close a window when it's deselcted. The
code I'm using at the moment is something like

<open window up here>

Repeat
  W=WaitEvent
  If W=$80000 AND EventWindow=1
    CloseWindow 1
  Endif
Forever

Which doesn't work. Any ideas?

Thanks
Neil

